Inputs
------
message : Vector
    The array of data to send to the CAN bus.
docstring.short_description: Send a message onto a CAN network through a slcan-compatible USB-to-CAN adapter.

parameters.name: arbitration_id
parameters.description: Unique ID for message being sent.
